@startuml
title MIU Food Browsing with Filtering

actor Customer
participant "Mobile/Web UI" as UI
box "MIU Food Ordering System"
    participant "RestaurantService" as RS
    participant "MenuService" as MS
    database "Database" as DB
end box

activate Customer
Customer -> UI: Clicks 'Browse Restaurants'

activate UI
UI -> RS: requestRestaurantList()
activate RS
RS -> DB: queryAllRestaurants()
activate DB
DB --> RS: return RestaurantList(Name, Cuisine, Rating)
deactivate DB

RS --> UI: displayRestaurantList
deactivate RS

UI -> Customer: Shows list of restaurants (US-C1)

Customer -> UI: Applies Filter (e.g., Cuisine='Italian') (US-C2)
UI -> RS: requestFilteredRestaurants(filterCriteria)
activate RS
RS -> DB: queryFilteredRestaurants(filterCriteria)
activate DB
DB --> RS: return FilteredRestaurantList
deactivate DB
RS --> UI: displayFilteredRestaurantList
deactivate RS

UI -> Customer: Shows filtered list

Customer -> UI: Selects a Restaurant (e.g., "Mama Mia's Pizza")
UI -> MS: requestMenu(restaurantId)
activate MS
MS -> DB: queryMenuItems(restaurantId)
activate DB
DB --> MS: return MenuItemList(Name, Price, Desc, Img, Ingredients)
deactivate DB
MS --> UI: displayMenuDetails
deactivate MS

UI -> Customer: Shows Menu with detailed items (US-C3, US-C4)
deactivate UI
deactivate Customer

@enduml